title: RIP MY SHRED STICK: GRAND HAVEN
description:
Another great day of RMSS in Grand Haven, Michigan. 48 degree water and flat conditions couldn't stop the fun from going down. Check the video highlights and head over to hurley.com/rmss for full schedule, photos and more info. 
Video: PK
